Aggregation.Name: Account Summarize
Aggregation.SQLExpression:
"N$10010" as (SELECT t0."ACCOUNT_ID", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_SUM", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_AVG", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_MIN", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_MAX", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_STDDEV", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_MEDIAN", t0."ORDER_ACCTO_CNT", t0."ORDER_BANKTO_CNT", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_SUM", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_SUM", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_SUM", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_SUM", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_CNT", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_CNT", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_CNT", t0."ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_CNT" FROM (SELECT "ACCOUNT_ID", SUM("AMOUNT") "ORDER_AMOUNT_SUM" ,AVG("AMOUNT") "ORDER_AMOUNT_AVG" ,MIN("AMOUNT") "ORDER_AMOUNT_MIN" ,MAX("AMOUNT") "ORDER_AMOUNT_MAX" ,STDDEV("AMOUNT") "ORDER_AMOUNT_STDDEV" ,MEDIAN("AMOUNT") "ORDER_AMOUNT_MEDIAN" ,COUNT(DISTINCT("ACCOUNT_TO")) "ORDER_ACCTO_CNT" ,COUNT(DISTINCT("BANK_TO")) "ORDER_BANKTO_CNT" ,SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Leasing' THEN "AMOUNT" ELSE 0 END) "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_SUM" ,SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Insurance Payment' THEN "AMOUNT" ELSE 0 END) "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_SUM" ,SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Household Payment' THEN "AMOUNT" ELSE 0 END) "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_SUM" ,SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Loan Payment' THEN "AMOUNT" ELSE 0 END) "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_SUM" ,SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Household Payment' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_CNT" ,SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Insurance Payment' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_CNT" ,SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Leasing' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_CNT" ,SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Loan Payment' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_CNT" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE}
GROUP BY "ACCOUNT_ID") t0 )

Source.Expression: SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Insurance Payment' THEN "AMOUNT" ELSE 0 END)
SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Household Payment' THEN "AMOUNT" ELSE 0 END)
SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Loan Payment' THEN "AMOUNT" ELSE 0 END)
SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Household Payment' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Insurance Payment' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
SUM(CASE WHEN "K_SYMBOL_BIN" = 'Loan Payment' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)

Transformation.Name: Order Type Recode
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10006" AS ( SELECT "ORDER_ID", "ACCOUNT_ID", "ACCOUNT_TO", "AMOUNT", "BANK_TO", case when "K_SYMBOL" is null then 'Null bin' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('LEASING') then 'Leasing' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('POJISTNE') then 'Insurance Payment' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('SIPO') then 'Household Payment' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('UVER') then 'Loan Payment' else 'Missing' end "K_SYMBOL_BIN" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

Transformation.Name: Loan Status Recode
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10014" AS ( SELECT "PAYMENTS", "ACCOUNT_ID", "AMOUNT", "LOAN_ID", "DURATION", case when "STATUS" is null then 'Null bin' when "STATUS" IN ('A') then 'Contract Finished, No Problem' when "STATUS" IN ('B') then 'Contract Finished, Not Payed' when "STATUS" IN ('C') then 'Contract Running, OK' when "STATUS" IN ('D') then 'Contract Running, Client in debt' else '<Other>' end "STATUS_BIN",TO_DATE("LOAN_DATE" ,'YYMMDD') - INTERVAL '100' YEAR(3) as "LOAN_DT" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

Transformation.Name: Ratio Calculation
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10016" AS ( SELECT "ACCOUNT_ID", "ORDER_AMOUNT_SUM", "ORDER_AMOUNT_AVG", "ORDER_AMOUNT_MIN", "ORDER_AMOUNT_MAX", "ORDER_AMOUNT_STDDEV", "ORDER_AMOUNT_MEDIAN", "ORDER_ACCTO_CNT", "ORDER_BANKTO_CNT", "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_SUM", "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_SUM", "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_SUM", "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_SUM", "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_CNT", "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_CNT", "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_CNT", "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_CNT",CASE WHEN "ORDER_AMOUNT_MAX" = 0 THEN 0 ELSE "ORDER_AMOUNT_AVG" / "ORDER_AMOUNT_MAX" END as "ORDER_AMT_AVG2MAX",CASE WHEN "ORDER_BANKTO_CNT" = 0 THEN 0 ELSE "ORDER_AMOUNT_SUM" / "ORDER_BANKTO_CNT" END as "ORDER_AMT_BANKTO_AVG",CASE WHEN "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_CNT" = 0 THEN 0 ELSE "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_SUM" / "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_CNT" END as "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_AVG",CASE WHEN "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_CNT" = 0 THEN 0 ELSE "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_SUM" / "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_CNT" END as "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_AVG",CASE WHEN "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_CNT" = 0 THEN 0 ELSE "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_SUM" / "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_CNT" END as "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_AVG",CASE WHEN "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_CNT" = 0 THEN 0 ELSE "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_SUM" / "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_CNT" END as "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_AVG",CASE WHEN "ORDER_AMOUNT_STDDEV" = 0 THEN 0 ELSE "ORDER_AMOUNT_AVG" / "ORDER_AMOUNT_STDDEV" END as "ORDER_AMOUNT_AVG2SD",CASE WHEN "ORDER_AMOUNT_MAX" = 0 THEN 0 ELSE "ORDER_AMOUNT_MIN" / "ORDER_AMOUNT_MAX" END as "ORDER_AMOUNT_MIN2MAX" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

Transformation.Name: Account Field Transform
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10021" AS ( SELECT "ACCOUNT_ID", "DISTRICT_ID", case when "FREQUENCY" is null then 'Null bin' when "FREQUENCY" IN ('POPLATEK MESICNE') then 'Monthly' when "FREQUENCY" IN ('POPLATEK PO OBRATU') then 'After Transaction' when "FREQUENCY" IN ('POPLATEK TYDNE') then 'Weekly' else '<Other>' end "FREQUENCY_BIN",TO_DATE("ACCOUNT_DATE",'YYMMDD') - INTERVAL '100' YEAR(3) as "ACCOUNT_DT" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

Transformation.Name: Client Gender And Birth Date
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10038" AS ( SELECT "ACCOUNT_ID", "OW_CLIENT_ID", "OW_DISP_ID", "DI_CLIENT_ID", "DI_DISP_ID", "OW_CL_DISTRICT_ID", "DI_CL_DISTRICT_ID",CASE WHEN "OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM" IS NULL THEN 'X' WHEN TO_NUMBER(SUBSTR("OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM",3,2)) > 50 THEN 'F' ELSE 'M' END as "OW_CL_GENDER",CASE WHEN "DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM" IS NULL THEN 'X' WHEN TO_NUMBER(SUBSTR("DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM",3,2)) > 50 THEN 'F' ELSE 'M' END as "DI_CL_GENDER",CASE WHEN "DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM" IS NOT NULL THEN TO_DATE( CASE WHEN TO_NUMBER(SUBSTR("DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM",3,2)) > 50 THEN "DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM" - 50 * 100 ELSE "DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM" END, 'YYMMDD') END - INTERVAL '100' YEAR(3) as "DI_CL_BIRTH_DT",CASE WHEN "OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM" IS NOT NULL THEN TO_DATE( CASE WHEN TO_NUMBER(SUBSTR("OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM",3,2)) > 50 THEN "OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM" - 50 * 100 ELSE "OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM" END, 'YYMMDD') END - INTERVAL '100' YEAR(3) as "OW_CL_BIRTH_DT" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

TransformationElementType.CustomTransformationEx: CASE WHEN "OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM" IS NULL THEN 'X' WHEN TO_NUMBER(SUBSTR("OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM",3,2)) > 50 THEN 'F' ELSE 'M' END
CASE WHEN "DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM" IS NULL THEN 'X' WHEN TO_NUMBER(SUBSTR("DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM",3,2)) > 50 THEN 'F' ELSE 'M' END

CASE WHEN "DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM" IS NOT NULL THEN TO_DATE( CASE WHEN TO_NUMBER(SUBSTR("DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM",3,2)) > 50 THEN "DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM" - 50 * 100 ELSE "DI_CL_BIRTH_NUM" END, 'YYMMDD') END - INTERVAL '100' YEAR(3)

CASE WHEN "OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM" IS NOT NULL THEN TO_DATE( CASE WHEN TO_NUMBER(SUBSTR("OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM",3,2)) > 50 THEN "OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM" - 50 * 100 ELSE "OW_CL_BIRTH_NUM" END, 'YYMMDD') END - INTERVAL '100' YEAR(3)

Transformation.Name: Card Field Transform
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10048" AS ( SELECT "DISP_ID", "CARD_ID", "TYPE",TO_TIMESTAMP("ISSUED",'YYMMDD HH24:MI:SS') - INTERVAL '100' YEAR(3) as "CARD_ISSUED_DATE" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

Transformation.Name: Flag Variables
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10055" AS ( SELECT "ACCOUNT_ID", "ACCOUNT_DT", "ORDER_AMOUNT_SUM", "ORDER_AMOUNT_AVG", "ORDER_AMOUNT_MIN", "ORDER_AMOUNT_MAX", "ORDER_AMOUNT_STDDEV", "ORDER_AMOUNT_MEDIAN", "ORDER_ACCTO_CNT", "ORDER_BANKTO_CNT", "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_SUM", "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_SUM", "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_SUM", "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_SUM", "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_CNT", "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_CNT", "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_CNT", "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_CNT", "ORDER_AMT_AVG2MAX", "ORDER_AMT_BANKTO_AVG", "ORDER_AMOUNT_HOU_AVG", "ORDER_AMOUNT_INS_AVG", "ORDER_AMOUNT_LEA_AVG", "ORDER_AMOUNT_LOA_AVG", "ORDER_AMOUNT_AVG2SD", "ORDER_AMOUNT_MIN2MAX", "LOAN_DT", "CARD_TYPE", "CARD_ISSUED_DATE", "CLIENT_US_DISTRICT_ID", "CLIENT_OWNER_BIRTH_DT", "LOAN_PAYMENTS", "ACCOUNT_FREQ", "LOAN_AMOUNT", "CLIENT_OWNER_GENDER", "LOAN_STATUS_BIN", "ACCOUNT_DISTRICT_ID", "CLIENT_OW_DISTRICT_ID", "CLIENT_USER_BIRTH_DT", "CLIENT_USER_GENDER", "LOAN_DURATION",CASE WHEN "CLIENT_USER_BIRTH_DT" IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END as "CLIENT_USER_FL",CASE WHEN "LOAN_DT" IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END as "LOAN_FL",CASE WHEN "ORDER_ACCTO_CNT" IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END as "ORDER_FL",CASE WHEN "CARD_ISSUED_DATE" IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END as "CARD_FL" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

TransformationElementType.CustomTransformationEx: CASE WHEN "CLIENT_USER_BIRTH_DT" IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END
CASE WHEN "LOAN_DT" IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END
CASE WHEN "ORDER_ACCTO_CNT" IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END
CASE WHEN "CARD_ISSUED_DATE" IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END
